OL,3,C'Vaping nearly killed me': The dangers
OL,4,Cof teenage vape use
OL,6,FAspiring boxer Ewan Fisher says that
OL,7,Fvaping nearly took his livelihood away
OL,8,Ffrom him, ITV News' Ben Chapman reports
OL,10,FVaping as a teenager left Ewan Fisher
OL,11,Funable to walk and with a 20% chance
OL,12,Fto live.
OL,14,F"It nearly killed me, put me on two
OL,15,Fdifferent life support machines, I was
OL,16,Fin an induced coma and I nearly lost
OL,17,Flife", Ewan told ITV News.
