OL,3,C'Vaping nearly killed me': The dangers
OL,4,Cof teenage vape use
OL,6,FAt the age of 16, Ewan was training to
OL,7,Fbecome a professional boxer and took
OL,8,Fup vaping to help him stop smoking
OL,9,Fcigarettes.
OL,11,FHowever, vaping caused Ewan to cough
OL,12,Fup bile and choke in his sleep so he
OL,13,Fwent into hospital, ultimately going
OL,14,Fonto life support.
OL,16,F"It was unbelievable. Obviously it was
OL,17,Fmore hurtful for my family than it was
OL,18,Ffor myself, because I wasn't with it
OL,19,Ffor most of that period," Ewan said.
