OL,6,F"I got put onto a ward for four or
OL,7,Ffive days, I just couldn't breathe at
OL,8,Fall at one point. So they rushed me on
OL,9,Fto intensive care and it got that bad
OL,10,Fthat they had to clear out all the
OL,11,Fparents and people off intensive care
OL,12,Fone evening to operate on me."
OL,14,FEwan was put onto an extracorporeal
OL,15,Fmembrane oxygenation, a lung bypass
OL,16,Fmachine, and put into an induced coma,
OL,17,Fbefore he was taken to a different
OL,18,Fhospital where a specialist team
OL,19,Fworked on him.
