OL,6,FHe was told that his lungs reacted to
OL,7,Fthe chemicals in the vape liquid.
OL,9,FEwan says that vaping nearly took his
OL,10,Flivelihood away from him.
OL,12,F"I couldn't walk, I couldn't fulfil my
OL,13,Fboxing career. I couldn't do anything,
OL,14,Freally. I didn't even get to sit my
OL,15,FGCSE exams. I had to sit maths and
OL,16,FEnglish a year after and miss the
OL,17,Frest. So it's made my life a struggle,
OL,18,Freally," he said.
