OL,3,C'Vaping nearly killed me': The dangers
OL,4,Cof teenage vape use
OL,6,FWhen asked what the appeal vaping is
OL,7,Ffor young people, Ewan said: "It's
OL,8,Fjust peer pressure and at that age,
OL,9,Fyou don't really think about how it's
OL,10,Fdamaging you or going to harm you long
OL,11,Fterm."
OL,13,FYoung people are being warned about
OL,14,Fvaping and nicotine addiction as part
OL,15,Fof a new government social media
OL,16,Fcampaign.
