OL,3,C'Vaping nearly killed me': The dangers
OL,4,Cof teenage vape use
OL,6,FThe 'Love Your Lungs' campaign, aimed
OL,7,Fat teenagers aged 13 to 18, is
OL,8,Flaunching on YouTube and Instagram and
OL,9,Fwill feature influencers including Big
OL,10,FManny and Bodalia.
OL,12,FAlongside the campaign, the government
OL,13,Fis supporting a new study tracking the
OL,14,Feffects of vaping on the health of
OL,15,F100,000 young people aged 8 to 18 over
OL,16,Fa 10-year period.
OL,18,FIt will collect health data as well as
OL,19,Fmonitoring information on wellbeing
OL,20,Fand other behaviours.
