OL,3,C'Vaping nearly killed me': The dangers
OL,4,Cof teenage vape use
OL,6,FSarah Sleet, chief executive at Asthma
OL,7,Fand Lung UK, said: "The number of non-
OL,8,Fsmokers, particularly young people,
OL,9,Ftaking up vaping is extremely
OL,10,Fworrying. The long-term impact of
OL,11,Fvaping on the lungs isn't yet known,
OL,12,Fso research into its effect on young
OL,13,Fpeople is really important."
OL,15,FThe study is one of three sets of
OL,16,Fresearch being commissioned by the
OL,17,Fgovernment into vaping.
