OL,3,C'Vaping nearly killed me': The dangers
OL,4,Cof teenage vape use
OL,6,FThe Tobacco and Vapes Bill, currently
OL,7,Fmaking its way through Parliament,
OL,8,Fwill look to clamp down on youth
OL,9,Fvaping by limiting flavours, packaging
OL,10,Fand displays deliberately designed to
OL,11,Fappeal to children.
OL,13,FFrom 1 June 2025, under separate
OL,14,Fenvironmental legislation, disposable
OL,15,Fvapes will be banned, reducing the
OL,16,Favailability and appeal of vapes to
OL,17,Fyoung people.
